{"tid":1812031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美海軍陸戰隊禁抖音 防中國竊情報","createTime":"2020-01-05T08:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T09:39:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2050fda2958357efd9f21e8724fdab22dd68c952","tid":1812031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200105/H3DRUEGXNPCUTROB7INYWBQ3PA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200105%2FH3DRUEGXNPCUTROB7INYWBQ3PA%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1WlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=9fff2b55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200105%2FH3DRUEGXNPCUTROB7INYWBQ3PA%2F&h=ac8ad186\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200105/H3DRUEGXNPCUTROB7INYWBQ3PA/</a><br />\n<br />\n美海軍陸戰隊禁抖音 防中國竊情報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200105/large/1578153306_0a78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200105%2Flarge%2F1578153306_0a78.jpg&h=838c3532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抖音曾被指收集用戶數據。<br />\n<br />\n美國繼續對中國進行科技封殺。繼美國海軍與陸軍先後禁止軍人使用抖音海外版TikTok後，美國的海軍陸戰隊也跟隨實行這個措施，聲稱要防止重要的軍事情報被中國盜走；另外美國商務部也頒令，限制特定科技出口國外，該項政策被指是針對中國。<br />\n<br />\n美國新聞網站TMZ本月2日引美國陸戰隊網絡空間司令部上尉亞歷杭德羅（Hector Alejandro）指，海軍陸戰隊成員不得在美國政府提供的手機使用TikTok，這是繼海軍和陸軍禁止後，再將禁令擴大。亞歷杭德羅補充指，「這個決定與我們一貫應對現存和正在湧現的威脅是一致的，我們正在保護與捍衞互聯網。」TMZ報道指，美國政界和軍方都擔心TikTok能搜集到美國人的情報。TikTok去年曾回應有關指控，指他們的美國用戶數據全部都儲存在美國境內，並在新加坡備份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n限制AI軟件出口<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國商務部在上周五（3日）也頒令，限制人工智能（AI）軟件出口海外，並會在明日生效。根據新措施，售賣特定類別地理空間圖像軟件的美國企業，在出口到外國前須先獲商務部批准，除非該國是加拿大。美國智庫戰略與國際研究中心（CSIS）科技專家形容，新措施包括用作自動識別目標的軟件，這些軟件可用於感應器、無人機及衞星。這項措施被視作針對中國的新措施。前年美國已通過法案，授權美國商務部制訂規則，加強監管敏感科技出口。<br />\n<br />\nTMZ/路透社"},{"pid":"52c1671e5f6bc793def7c3436eb3115a34b1b9e7","tid":1812031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:22:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">銅鑼灣 x 灣仔稅局 和你Lunch</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月6日 星期一<br />\n時間 ： 1245 <br />\n地點 ：時代廣場集合/灣仔稅務局<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港保險仝人職工會 + 香港音樂人工會 招募會員聯合街站</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月6日 星期一<br />\n時間 ： 1200-1500<br />\n地點 ：觀塘巧明街/駿業街Walking East 雕塑"},{"pid":"9df229b17daa9bfe9c4d3f5b7db3b54738b8a0c5","tid":1812031,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />圍堵支那"},{"pid":"17f36ee28b2b9e6bfd6f39a854ce857a55e97d44","tid":1812031,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接搞鳩間公司？好似係騰訊下話？"},{"pid":"a6008c4d633e1ce5e90ad496606a9faf2b58ba90","tid":1812031,"uid":184050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:31:28.000Z","msg":"終於禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人再玩，就嚟成個USMC 資料送比中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d166d540d371c5dbe3ab481b562e1b99b70cf11","tid":1812031,"uid":224533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:32:59.000Z","msg":"美國要好好教育啲鬼仔鬼妹咪撚再玩抖音"},{"pid":"b8f6a7f310918b388bd851bed1a0028db7525ed4","tid":1812031,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17f36ee28b2b9e6bfd6f39a854ce857a55e97d44","tid":1812031,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接搞鳩間公司？好似係騰訊下話？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"字節跳動，唔係企鵝"},{"pid":"2702ab9c59fa3e283d350c4d92da6544f7535f30","tid":1812031,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f6a7f310918b388bd851bed1a0028db7525ed4","tid":1812031,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco